OL,3,CPrison for Uber Eats driver who raped
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman
OL,6,FAn Uber Eats delivery driver who
OL,7,Freturned to a customer's address in
OL,8,FBoston and raped her after a delivery
OL,9,Fhas been jailed.
OL,11,FJitendrakumar Prajapati had delivered
OL,12,Ffood to the woman on 19 January when
OL,13,Fhe struck up conversation with her,
OL,14,Fbefore returning several hours later
OL,15,Fand attacking her.
OL,17,FThe 47-year-old had told the woman he
OL,18,Fhad just moved to the area and didn't
OL,19,Fknow anyone, and needed help getting a
OL,20,Fvisa and to work.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
