FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774959066
OL,3,CPrison for Uber Eats driver who raped
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman
OL,6,FLincoln Crown Court heard he asked for
OL,7,Fthe victim's Instagram account
OL,8,Fdetails, and they swapped phone
OL,9,Fnumbers, playing on the good nature of
OL,10,Fthe victim - to be able to keep in
OL,11,Ftouch about helping him with his visa
OL,12,Fapplication.
OL,14,FHe returned to the property at around
OL,15,F5pm the same day where they talked for
OL,16,Fa while before things took a sinister
OL,17,Fturn and he raped his victim.
OL,19,FAfter leaving the victim's home, he
OL,20,Fsent a message to her saying, "Hey I
OL,21,Fam sorry".
OL,26,@|D@_OU}D@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
