PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774959066
OL,3,CPrison for Uber Eats driver who raped
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman
OL,6,FHe then changed his WhatsApp username
OL,7,Fand enabled 'disappearing chat after
OL,8,F24 hours'. More messages were
OL,9,Fexchanged where the victim accused him
OL,10,Fof raping her. His responses were
OL,11,Fapologetic and begging her not to tell.
OL,13,FHe arrested the same day at around
OL,14,F9pm, on suspicion of rape and non-
OL,15,Ffatal strangulation, a charge which
OL,16,Fwas later dropped at court.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
