OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774959066
OL,3,CPrison for Uber Eats driver who raped
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman
OL,6,FThe detective investigating this case,
OL,7,FDetective Constable Jessica McKiernan,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Bringing this offender to
OL,9,Fjustice was made possible by the
OL,10,Fextraordinary courage shown by the
OL,11,Fvictim in coming forward at the
OL,12,Fearliest opportunity.
OL,14,F"Her trust in us allowed our officers
OL,15,Fto begin swift and focused inquiries,
OL,16,Fwhich led to the suspect being located
OL,17,Fwithin hours. Her bravery has been
OL,18,Fvital in ensuring he is now held to
OL,19,Faccount. We hope this outcome offers
OL,20,Fher some sense of reassurance as she
OL,21,Fmoves forward on her own terms."
OL,26,@pD@GOU}D@`O]
