OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774959066
OL,3,CPrison for Uber Eats driver who raped
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman
OL,6,FPrajapati, of Castle Square, Wyberton
OL,7,FWest Road, Boston was jailed for three
OL,8,Fyears and eight months on Friday after
OL,9,Fpleading guilty to rape.
OL,11,FHe was was also sentenced concurrently
OL,12,Ffor 18 months for sexual assault and
OL,13,Fserved a deportation order.
OL,15,FLincolnshire Police offer support for
OL,16,Fthose in immediate danger, seeking
OL,17,Femotional help, or looking for
OL,18,Fconfidential specialist services for
OL,19,Fyourself or someone you are worried
OL,20,Fabout.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
